name: Micheline Guyot
description: I am looking for a man who will change my world, who will bring me so much interest in life and who will bring more happiness than what I have now. I am looking for a man who can love me more than everything and will give importance to me as always, who will make me feel like he is close to me always even when we are far from each other.I’m looking for a man who will love me forever. Someone who’s loving, caring, understanding, patient and very sweet to me all the time. I want a man who knows how to respect and treat a woman right. Someone who’s honest, loyal and faithful. All that matters is that he’s a good and well-off person. A man whom I can be with for the rest of my life and will never ever let me go.
